        <li><a href="/guides/" class="hover:text-blue-600 transition">Guides</a></li><li>›</li>
        <li class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-medium">JSON formatting best practices for debugging and delivery</li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

